1. *Molim* te da mi pomogneš. (I ask you to help me.)
2. Šta *molim*? (What am I asking?)
3. *Molim* vas da zaustavite javni prevoz. (I ask you to stop the public transport.)
4. Poštovanje, *molim* vas da me obavestite o tome. (Respectfully, I ask you to inform me about it.)
5. *Molim* te da mi daš još jednu šansu. (I ask you to give me another chance.)